data.text:
Spider-Man: The Animated Series lasted for five season and consists of sixty five episodes that were aired from 1994 to 1998.

Series overview[]

Season Episodes First aired Last aired 1 13 November 19, 1994 June 11, 1995 2 14 September 9, 1995 February 24, 1996 3 14 April 27, 1996 November 23, 1996 4 11 February 1, 1997 August 2, 1997 5 13 September 12, 1997 January 31, 1998

Trivia[]

All the episodes from season 2 had a Neogenic Nightmare chapter prefix to it.

All episodes from season 3 had a The Sins of the Fathers chapter prefix to it.

Only eight episodes from season 3 actually dealt with sins that were committed by by fathers.
